### ğŸ” Authentication

* `POST /api/auth/register/`
* `POST /api/auth/login/`

### ğŸ‘¤ Patients (Authenticated)

* `POST /api/patients/`
* `GET /api/patients/`
* `GET /api/patients/<id>/`
* `PUT /api/patients/<id>/`
* `DELETE /api/patients/<id>/`

### ğŸ‘¨â€âš•ï¸ Doctors (Authenticated)

* `POST /api/doctors/`
* `GET /api/doctors/`
* `GET /api/doctors/<id>/`
* `PUT /api/doctors/<id>/`
* `DELETE /api/doctors/<id>/`

### ğŸ”— Mappings

* `POST /api/mappings/`
* `GET /api/mappings/`
* `DELETE /api/mappings/<id>/`

